tags.description: Located near the entrance to the Tehaleh® community, Ponder Park is be the perfect spot to read a good book, enjoy the tranquil pond, the local artwork or connect to one of your favorite Tehaleh community trails.
tags.name: Ponder Park

tags.description: Playground, picnic spot, climbable boulders, and grassy domes. Featuring spectacular views of Mt. Rainier.
tags.name: Boulder Dash

tags.description: Yonder is a quiet place to relax, especially after hiking the amazing trail system in Tehaleh. Toward evening, you might hear a chorus of croaking frogs in the pond that is only rivaled by the crickets.
tags.name: Yonder Park
